snippet.title: Digimon World Next Order - PS4 - The Digi'Hunt begins (English Trailer)
snippet.description:
Digimon World Next Order is coming 27 January 2017 on PS4! Join our online Digi'Hunt and capture Digimon to reveal the secret message! More info at: http://bnent.eu/digihunt. Did you find the first DigiCard hidden in the trailer? ;)
